docs {
  ## Delete Product Item Group
  ลบกลุ่มรายการสินค้าตาม ID

  Removes a product item group from the system.

  ### Path Parameters
  - `id` — Product Item Group UUID (รหัสกลุ่มรายการสินค้า)


  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "message": "Success"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}

